'''Balinquar's Virus''' was a fictitious disease that supposedly affected [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Arkanian/Legends|Arkanian]] offshoots when they reached old age, caused paranoia, and could be deadly. [[Arkoh Adasca]] claimed that [[Gorman Vandrayk|Camper]] was infected with it, but, later, in private conversation with [[Demagol|Antos Wyrick]], masquerading as [[Rohlan Dyre]], it was revealed to be a ruse designed to separate Camper from [[Jarael]].

